(3590,1,"2018-07-14 13:30:15","2018-07-14 13:30:15","[social_icons_group id=\"3968\"]\r\n\r\nWelcome to the Iron Works Gym in Gothenburg!\r\n\r\nWelcome to one of Gothenburg\'s absolute most modern training facilities. With an area of over 1500 m2, we have everything you can imagine for your training. The gym is divided into 2 floors where the upstairs houses our state-of-the-art machinery. There you will find machines and accessories from Hoist, Hammer Strength, MAG, Life Fitness and much more. Downstairs we have thought of you who like heavy lifting with free weights. There you can enjoy brand new Eleonosticks with associated weights for your knees or marklift. Are you more for machines, it\'s no problem. We have leg machines and much more on our lower level too! In the other gym you will also find Solarium, Children\'s Room, Nutritional Store, Massage, Posing Room, and a really nice atmosphere, whether you are a beginner or a professional!\r\n\r\nAnnual memberships and direct debit members can also visit other gyms around Sweden through KlubbSverige Mobil.\r\n\r\n<h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>\r\n<strong>How to get your membership?</strong>\r\nYou can get your membership in just three easy steps:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Purchase your gym membership here on <strong>guineapig</strong>pig.</li>\r\n 	<li>You will get a receipt of this purchase sent to your email.</li>\r\n 	<li>Walk into your gym and show the receipt in the reception. The receptionist will then be able to add you to their system knowing that you have paid for your membership on<strong>guinea</strong>pig<strong>.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3>Maps</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/embed?mid=11CnM-jh0MnumjwONS19FdmHSOAyc94vH\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\r\n","Iron Works Membership","Welcome to Iron Works Gym Gothenburg!","publish","open","closed","","iron-works-membership","","","2018-07-15 18:57:05","2018-07-15 18:57:05","",0,"https://guineapig.local/?post_type=produ