(3723,1,"2018-07-14 17:18:13","2018-07-14 17:18:13","[social_icons_group id=\"4076\"]\r\n\r\nHow do we think? Our vision at Crossfit Loket is that everyone will get the best opportunity to reach their training goals and get a wonderful community in one package!\r\n\r\nAt CrossFit Loket, we focus on the development of each individual. We train in a developing way along with many talented instructors and athletes with different experiences. Our training should be fun, efficient, challenging and always scalable for each individual.\r\n\r\nIn the class, we mix Olympic lifting, rowing, jumping, gymnastics and pure strength training. This is to create the most effective and varied exercise.\r\n\r\nGood technique: It is important that you first learn to perform the exercise correctly and safely, so that by increasing the speed you get the positive effect it gives to exercise under higher intensity. The coaches are there to ensure that the load and exercise are adjusted to your requirements so that the training is safe, fun and rewarding.\r\n\r\nWorkout of the day (WOD): We always start with common warming that is combined with different exercises and adapted to how today\'s WOD looks. After warming and mobility that takes about 15 minutes, we take the time to go through the different movements and train the technique on the exercises to be performed in the WOD. The pass ends with joint stretching.\r\n\r\nGetting Started: The best way is to try it out. After that you have the opportunity to go to our basic class and also our introductory course which is compulsory for those who want to work with us at the Crossfit Loket. We have running courses so check out our website and follow us on facebook so you do not miss a chance.\r\n\r\nIn our box everyone is welcome! We have athletes of different ages, with different experiences and different backgrounds. Despite our differences, we have a great community that we are very proud of! We have no place for big egos or boring attitudes. Rather, we only have place for development and fun workout.\r\n\r\nWelcome to the Crossfit Loket!\r\n<h3>Maps</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/embed?mid=1PQNUa--n49W03lxG3B4BJAMjhaDtNOTC\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>","CrossFit Loket","Our vision at Crossfit Loket is that everyone will get the best opportunity to reach their training goals and get a wonderful community in the box in one package!","publish","open","closed","","crossfit-loket","","","2018-07-15 18:56:10","2018-07-15 18:56:10","",0,"https://guineapig.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=3723",0,"product","",0),
