(3752,1,"2018-07-14 18:22:37","2018-07-14 18:22:37","[social_icons_group id=\"4090\"]\r\n\r\nFriskis&amp;Svettis Kungsbacka can be found in two premises: Kabelgatan 8, and Storgatan 21 in the inner city. On Kabelgatan we have a large gym, a circuit gym, all our group training, children\'s rooms, caf, sale of clothes and gadgets as well as dressing rooms, sauna and a place to relax for women and men. In the inner city you can find our newest gym with dressing rooms for men and women. Our membership cards are of course valid in both premises. Both of our premises now also have tenants in the form of hired massage therapists. The association was formed in 1989. In 2004, we acquired our own premises, which meant a huge boost and a doubling of the number of members in just one year. Since then, the development has gone fast and today we have over 3,500 square meters, including three halls for group training in various forms, a large spinning hall with 50 spin cycles and a separate hall for indoor walking. The premises also include over 1 300 m2 for nice gym training!\r\n\r\nNOTE! Everyone who has a membership with us is a member of an ideal association: IF Friskis &amp; Svettis in Kungsbacka. The membership fee is 100 SEK and is paid per calendar year. This means that regardless of when you buy your training card, we will charge your membership fee for the current year. In January, all members must pay their membership fee for the new year. However, we are starting to sell the membership fee for the following year, already in November, to avoid jams and congestion in January. If you have not paid your membership fee, you can not withdraw your membership card in the vending machine and get a receipt, but you are instead referred to the Member Service. As a member you will receive an accident insurance covering damage that occurs under any of our classes.\r\n\r\nOn Kabelgatan we have a manned reception during all opening hours:\r\nMon-Thurs 6.00-21.30\r\nFri 6.00-20.00\r\nSat-Sun 8.00-21.00\r\n\r\nOn Storgatan we have open 4.30-23.30 every day with manned reception some hours each day (with reservation for illness):\r\nMon &amp; Thurs 16.00-21.30\r\nTue Wed 17.00-21.30\r\nFri 16.00-20.00\r\nSat-Sun 10.00-13.00\r\n\r\nPrices &amp; membership guide:\r\nAll-Card - Applies to our entire range of services. Available for 1, 6 and 12 months.\r\nGym Card - Only valid in the gym and for pure circuit training.\r\nGroup Training Card - Applies to anything but the gym. In other words, you can practice both gymnastics, spinning, indoor walking with several group training classes and all variants of combo and outdoor classes on this card.\r\nDaytime Card - Applies to our entire range, Mon-Sun from the time we open until 15:00.\r\n<h3>Maps</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/embed?mid=1HCPNXigRcjsJv-16lBy0WnQFvz_AWOBp\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>","Friskis&Svettis Kungsbacka","For you and all you want to do.","publish","open","closed","","friskissvettis-kungsbacka","","","2018-07-15 18:55:42","2018-07-15 18:55:42","",0,"https://guineapig.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=3752",0,"product","",0),
