gskeppet, Sthlm Kickboxning, Allstar Training Center, The box / Southside Muaythai\n\n<strong>Swimming:</strong> Eriksdalsbadet, Human Ambition, Kronobergsbadet, Sundbybergs Simhall\n\n<strong>Climbing:</strong> Klttercentret (Akalla, Solna, Telefonplan)\n\n<strong>Racket sports:</strong> PDL Center, Sundbybergs Rackethall, Enskede Rakethall, Court1 Padel Club\n\n<strong>Spinning:</strong> Urban Ride, Najaden, Miramar, X-force\n\n<strong>Running:</strong> Viscus Running, Club Running\n\n<strong>Alternative training:</strong> Studio DQ, Acid Training, Bounce, Nordic Military Training, Rlis Kajak &amp; SUP, Break it make it, Evolve Fitness, Drivkraft, Extremfabriken, Gatti Training, Ruffie Training, Studio levels, Team Nordic Trail, Under construction, Workout The Studio\n\n<strong>GOTHENBURG</strong>\n\n<strong>CrossFit:</strong> 421 Crossfit, Bunkern, CF Vstkusten Landvetter / Mlnlycke, CrossFit Grda\n\n<strong>Yoga / Dancing:</strong> Arken, Bikram Yoga, Eminent, Lilla Lotus, Mediyoga Institutet, Mindful Yoga, Yoga Centrum, Yoga GBG, Nia Movement, Trningsverket, Viscus, Hela Hlsan, Danzlagret, Sknhetsfabriken, Yogabylink, Yoga Treats, Yogayama\n\n<strong>Gym / Fitness:</strong> Aveny Gym, Beach Center, Bunkern, Exhale Hardcore Gym, Fighter Center Gym, Hela Hlsan, Kettlebell Center, The OCR Gym, World Class Klippan, Iron Works Gym, Lindome Gym &amp; Hlsa, Sknhetsfabriken, Trningsverket, Friskis &amp; Svettis (Askim, Eriksberg, Grda, Johannesberg, Kortedala, Kungsgatan, Kvillebcken, Lackarebck, Majorna, Mlnlycke, Torslanda)\n\n<strong>Martial Arts:</strong> Fit4Fight Gym, GBG MMA, United MMA\n\n<strong>Swimming:</strong> Valhallabadet\n\n<strong>Climbing:</strong> Kltterfabriken\n\n<strong>Racket sports:</strong> Padel Center, Gteborg Lawn Tennis Club\n\n<strong>Alternative training:</strong> Military Fitness, OCR Ninja Center, Polestar Fitness, Aktivitus, Arken, Beach Center, Gympro, Kettlebell Center, OCR Fltet, OCR &amp; Ninja Center, Point65 Kayak Center, The OCR