ited=\"on|desktop\" module_class=\"about-page-content\" _builder_version=\"3.9\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" padding_tablet=\"30px|0px|0px|0px\" padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" padding_bottom=\"30px\" padding_left=\"50px\" padding_right=\"50px\" padding_top=\"75px\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text h1 header\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" header_font=\"|700|||||||\" header_font_size=\"35px\" header_font_size_tablet=\"33px\" header_font_size_phone=\"27px\" header_font_size_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_margin=\"||20px|\"]<h1>Our Mission</h1>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"3.9\"]<p>At <strong>guinea</strong>pig, we want to help people to understand and improve their health and fitness.We are pursuing the third SDG (Sustainable Development Goal) from the <a href=\"https://www.un.org/sustainabledevelopment/health/\">United Nations</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"Ensure healthy lives and promote well-being for all at all ages.\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>If you want to join us on this mission, you can do so in three simple ways:</p>\n<p>1. Work to understand and improve your own health and fitness, as well as the health and fitness of your friends, family, and community. We are hard at work to help you do this with<strong>guinea</strong>pig.</p>\n<p>2. Partner with <strong>guinea</strong>pig to offer your health and fitness products and services on our marketplace.</p>\n<p>3. Come and work with us at <strong>guinea</strong>pig! We need all the help we can get to pursue this moonshot mission.</p>\n<p>We can\'t wait to hear which path you choose.</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text - signature\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" text_font=\"Reenie Beanie||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#232323\" text_font_size=\"45px\" text_line_height=\"1.1\" text_orientation=\"right\" module_alignment=\"right\" custom_margin=\"20px|||\"]<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Elias &amp; Anton</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" bg_img=\"https://guineapig.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/guineapig-large.png\" background_color=\"#f9f9f9\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" background_position=\"center\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" custom_padding=\"0px|||\"][et_pb_row custom_padding=\"||10px|\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Default Header\" module_class=\"default-header\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" module_alignment=\"right\"]<h1>Our Vision</h1>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row use_custom_gutter=\"on\" gutter_width=\"3\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"3.0.89\"]<p>At <strong>guinea</strong>pig, we are building the world\'s best marketplace to buy, sell, and use health and fitness products and services.</p>\n<p>Our startup was born out of Chalmers School of Entrepreneurship at Chalmers University of Technology. Today, we are enrolled in the accelerator program at Chalmers Ventures and are working to grow our marketplace every day.</p>\n<p>If you believe in our vision and want to work with us as an intern, thesis writer, employee, partner, or investor, then we\'d love to talk to you! Get in touch by phone, email, or our chat and we will get back to you as soon as we can.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb title=\"The problem\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%164%%\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" icon_font_size=\"35px\" admin_label=\"About Blurb\" module_class=\"about-page-blurb\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" header_font=\"|600|||||||\" header_line_height=\"1.2\"]<p>Toensure healthy lives and promote well-being for all at all ages.</p>[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb title=\"Chalmers University of Technology and Chalmers Ventures\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%155%%\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" icon_font_size=\"35px\" admin_label=\"About Blurb\" module_class=\"about-page-blurb\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" header_font=\"|600|||||||\" header_line_height=\"1.2\"]<p>We are working top nordic universities and investors.</p>[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb title=\"The solution\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%169%%\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" icon_font_size=\"35px\" admin_label=\"About Blurb\" module_class=\"about-page-blurb\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" header_font=\"|600|||||||\" header_line_height=\"1.2\"]<p>The world\'s best marketplace to buy, sell, and use health and fitness products and services.</p>[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb title=\"Join us\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%101%%\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" icon_font_size=\"35px\" admin_label=\"About Blurb\" module_class=\"about-page-blurb\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" header_font=\"|600|||||||\" header_line_height=\"1.2\"]<p>We are always looking for passionate people to join us. We can\'t wait to hear from you!</p>[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" custom_padding=\"0px|||\"][et_pb_row custom_padding=\"||10px|\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\"